# Trivy suppressions for Wave 5.
#
# These are base-image distro CVEs inherited from nginx:1.27-alpine3.19.
# The Alpine security team has pushed fixes; upgrading the base image to
# alpine3.20+ picks them up. Alpine 3.20 has a known pyexpat ABI issue with
# Python 3.12 that broke an earlier Wave — we'll re-evaluate once the upstream
# nginx image publishes a 3.21 variant that avoids it.
#
# Deadline: review by 2026-05-15 — bump base image or accept.
# Tracking: tasks/review-2026-04-22.md (H-DOCKERFILE-TAG / devops Round 2).

# libxml2 + libxslt (base: alpine3.19)
CVE-2024-55549
CVE-2025-24855

# musl / musl-utils (base: alpine3.19)
CVE-2025-26519
CVE-2026-40200

# xz-libs (base: alpine3.19)
CVE-2025-31115
